data.description: RENOVATED MAIN LEVEL home on private 1 acre lot. Nestled at the end of the road. METAL ROOF 1 year old. Hot water heater 2 yr old. New subfloors with laminate hardwoods and tile. New interior and exterior paint.  Recessed lighting and smooth ceilings. New windows. Great room with abundant, natural light and fireplace. Good size 3 bedrooms with some built ins and ceiling fans. Gorgas Bathroom with shower. Nice size Kitchen features updated appliances, gas stove, eat in area and new ceiling. Laundry room with barn doors and built in storage.  30 x 30 Work shop with 2 garage doors, electricity, concrete floors, water access and separate drive way. Two additional storage buildings in the back to remain with a concrete patio area. SPACIOUS front porch. DON'T MISS THIS ONE !!!
